title: Overselling Joy (feat. Rosebud Baker & Andy Haynes)
description: Newlywed comics Rosebud Baker and Andy Haynes joined the show and discussed the roles they get cast for and the hurt feelings that ensue. Jay is floored as Rosebud reveals what's in store for him at an upcoming comedy gig. Overselling your moan can have some long lasting damage.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
